wkk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Cooking eggs is hard</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tToKLTj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I mean, safer than the alternative?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/crxrqas.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>If you can dodge a wrench...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2OoukOH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Weird that my resting heart rate is that of someone being hunted for sport, right?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/mtl7Puy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>All fun and games until is sets the ficus on fire</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3Bx8zeu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>We have a jar for bad jokes at work</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/r4hYguy.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And this was pre pandemic behavior</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/vrL1w59.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Text for no ads</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/BX2p9NN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Actually grew up near this. Sad times in funtown</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MK97J39.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>If everyone is a bad influence are you all good influences?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/2iS16HL.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>By Talos this can't be happening</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VIvsFWH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>There was an attempt</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/31Sqmwd.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>go back to school for more debt or work this dead-end job forever</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wgIAwvY.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>50/50 I still miss it</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/0l4KVDj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>What we call pro gaming moves</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LcG1M1N.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Did I steal this line for my paladin? No, I can't roll high enough to hit things</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/nPBkSMc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Just an exhausting time</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/At06zEM.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It's probably fine</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/obwZBlc.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Worked in a hospital for a while and uh, yeah. Never quite that bad</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/jgBvOuJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>End on a high note. Be excellent to each other.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/WAd6WHg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Niffy tax. I promise he's actually photogenic, honest</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/yEjJk2T</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[formerlyknownashades]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>PSA!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/F9d7FZA</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6bKARU7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Wow, front page and an a